<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Description==
</div>

[[Image:TechDraw_FillTemplateFields.svg|24px]][[TechDraw_FillTemplateFields|填充模板字段]]工具使用[[Std_ProjectInfo|文档信息]]中的内容填充当前页面模板内的可编辑文本字段。

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
[[Image:TD_fill_template_fields.JPG|500px]]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Usage==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Before starting the tool, create a page with the selected template and add a view.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_FillTemplateFields.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_FillTemplateFields|Update Template Fields]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Page → [[Image:TechDraw_FillTemplateFields.svg|16px]] Update Template Fields}} option from the menu.
# The ''Fill Template Fields in Page'' window will appear.
# Deselect the ''Update'' checkboxes next to fields that you don't want to update. You can also use the ''Update All'' checkbox to enable and disable all fields. Optionally, edit the strings shown on the right if you want to modify the data taken from document information.
# Press {{Button|Ok}} to update the fields or {{Button|Cancel}} to discard the changes.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Notes==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* This tool relies on the {{FileName|FillTemplateFields.csv}} spreadsheet file in the FreeCAD installation directory under {{FileName|.../share/Mod/TechDraw/CSVdata}}.
* {{Version|1.0}}: There is also the [[TechDraw_Templates#Description|autofill tool]].
</div>


